arts.ttl: Crystal Palace vs Fredrikstad – Match preview and team news
arts.sum: Crystal Palace make their European debut on Thursday night, hosting Fredrikstad in the first leg of the UEFA Europa Conference League playoff round. The Eagles are entering continental competition for the first time in their history and will be determined to secure a commanding lead at Selhurst Park against their Norwegian opponents.
